Installation

- Download and install the Libraries (7.x-2.x branch) module
http://drupal.org/project/libraries

- Download and install Rackspace's PHP API binding and place it in sites/all/libraries/rackspacecloudfies/
(sites/all/libraries/rackspacecloudfies/php-cloudfiles/cloudfiles.php)
https://github.com/rackspace/php-cloudfiles/

- Configure your setttings at /admin/config/cloud-files/settings

- Visit admin/config/media/file-system and set the Default download method to Rackspace Cloud Files

- Add a field of type File or Image etc and set the Upload destination to Rackspace Cloud Files in the Field Settings tab.